#The Fall of the Bureaucrats

           -
##### This papertoy exhibition shows my recent works made with papertoys, or inspired by them. Exhibition is centered around installation "The Fall of Bureaucrats", work are form Blockheads, Disoriented Series. It's main character is Anonymous Official, which takes roles of anonymous lobbyists, businessmen and investors, art critics and collectors, politics and bureaucrats of centralized systems in general and they are all put in various animated papertoy scenes. This exhibition is actually a virtual version of the cancelled show I was supposed to have in April, in MMC Gallery in Umag, Croatia. The exhibition was cancelled due to Covid-19 and in this virtual version, few other papertoy projects are featured, like CryptoPapertoys, inspired by cryptocurrencies and Perodrillo papertoys, made out from visual conversation between seven artists on DADA.art platform.
